membership:
UCT Prague is a member of the European University Association, ECTN (European Chemistry Thematic Network), the European Federation of National Engineering Associations, and the International Society for Engineering Pedagogy. &#xd;
Department of International Relations is a member of the EAIE (European Association for International Education) and coordinates the activities for UCT Prague in the networks Study in the Czech Republic and Study in Prague.&#xd;
UCT Prague faculties are active members of a number of international organisations and networks both on educational and research level. Besides, there are professional associations which UCT Prague staff are members of, for example European Federation of Chemical Engineering (www.efce.info).
